Sunday August 18th 2013 11:29 pm -04:00,First time I heard of BODMAS in Canada its BEDMAS - E standing for Exponents. Although in the end its the same thing. Just remember that Multiplication/Divison have equal precedence as does Addition/Subtraction. So 10-3+2=9 (not 5). Think of it as 10+(-3)+2. Example from Wikipedia., Resolved,3
